      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Suggested Sequence\n\n## Phase 1\n- define the knowledge skill contract\n- map the current Knowledge / Research graph into it\n- decide provenance repair boundaries\n\n## Phase 2\n- implement validation for membership and provenance drift\n- wire graph-local reporting\n- test on the current nodeset graph\n\n## Phase 3\n- implement bounded repairs for metadata and summary drift\n- keep claim and evidence meaning out of auto-rewrite scope\n- generalize later only after the local pilot is legible",
